Package: giphypraise
Type: Package
Title: Praise users with gifs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Greg", "Freedman Ellis", email = "greg.freedman@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: giphypraise is an R package that combines the praise package with the giphy api. 
    It parses a string to add positive words using the praise package, 
    then searches giphy for a gif using one of those words.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: htmltools,
    httr, 
    knitr, 
    magrittr,
    praise
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
